title: Star Wars - Racer [PC] [ENGLISH] [ISO] + Win7 Installer
description:
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS


 1. Mount Star Wars - Racer on a virtual drive (DO NOT INSTALL IT!)
 2. After mounting SW-R, run the "graphics patch" this small program will help you install the game and run it on modern computers.
 3. Play!


IMPORTANT NOTE!


 Do not mount the game on a different drive then the one you have installed it from, otherwise the game won't run and it will keep asking you for the CD.


WORKS ON WINDOWS 7 & 8!


Enjoy & Seed!
